USivuyisile Mtshali (32) uthole udilikajele ngecala lokubulala, emihlanu ngokuthumba, emihlanu ngelokuzama ukubulala iphoyisa, emine ngelokuzama ukubulala ilungu lomphakathi nemithathu ngelokutholakala nesikhali esiyingozi. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, uthe uMtshali waboshwa ngemuva kokushaya owayeyintombi yakhe, wamhudulela endlini yakhe. “Ilungu lomphakathi lazama ukumvimba waligeja ngommese. Wahudulela umgilwa endlini yakhe, wamgwaza ngomkhonto,” kusho uCaptain Gwala. Uthe ngesikhathi kuthintwa amaphoyisa aseMzimkhulu, uMtshali wajijimeza elinye ngomkhonto lasinda ngokulambisa. Uthe wazama ukuzinquma kodwa wabanjwa waphuthunyiswa esibhedlela lapho elashwe khona ngaphambi kokuboshwa.